- Oh, cool.

11:08.292 --> 11:10.378
All right,
should we go to bed?

11:10.461 --> 11:12.588
- I guess so.

11:12.671 --> 11:14.173
{\an3}- All right,
good night, Bill.

11:14.256 --> 11:16.217
- Good night.

