<i>while we hung back</i>

01:08:52.837 --> 01:08:55.214
<i>so she wouldn't be startled</i>
<i>by the cameras.</i>

01:08:55.296 --> 01:08:58.216
{\an3}This is it.

01:09:02.513 --> 01:09:03.930
It's right down there.

01:09:04.014 --> 01:09:06.183
- Oh. Okay.

01:09:12.356 --> 01:09:15.024
[both chuckle]

01:09:15.109 --> 01:09:16.694
It's right
down there.

01:09:16.777 --> 01:09:18.153
{\an3}- Yeah.

01:09:18.237 --> 01:09:21.198
{\an1}- [laughs]

01:09:21.282 --> 01:09:23.868
{\an1}Oh, Lord.
God have mercy.

01:09:23.951 --> 01:09:26.287
{\an1}[laughs]

01:09:26.370 --> 01:09:28.330
{\an3}- [laughs]

01:09:28.413 --> 01:09:30.332
<i>But when it came time</i>
<i>to get out,</i>

01:09:30.416 --> 01:09:32.334
<i>Bill didn't want to go down</i>
<i>without us.</i>

01:09:32.417 --> 01:09:34.377
{\an1}- Well, I thought--
wouldn't you want it that way

01:09:34.461 --> 01:09:36.505
with the cameras?

01:09:36.589 --> 01:09:38.883
{\an3}- Well, it seems like
a personal moment for you.

01:09:38.966 --> 01:09:41.510
- Oh, bring
the cameras.

01:09:41.594 --> 01:09:44.513
I like all the PR.

01:09:46.640 --> 01:09:47.765
{\an1}[laughs]

01:09:47.850 --> 01:09:49.935
{\an1}You heard it,
the PR.

01:09:50.019 --> 01:09:52.688
- What do you mean?

01:09:52.770 --> 01:09:56.066
{\an1}- Public relations,
PR.

01:09:56.150 --> 01:09:58.527
-<i> And it concerned me</i>
<i>that Bill didn't realize</i>

01:09:58.611 --> 01:10:01.071
<i>how showing up at her front</i>
<i>door with a camera crew</i>

01:10:01.155 --> 01:10:02.865
<i>might freak her out.</i>

01:10:02.948 --> 01:10:04.909
{\an3}What do you think
it'll be like for her?

01:10:04.992 --> 01:10:07.161
{\an1}- I--she wouldn't
mind it.

01:10:07.244 --> 01:10:08.996
- The cameras?

01:10:09.079 --> 01:10:10.789
{\an1}- Right.

01:10:10.873 --> 01:10:12.791
-<i> If he really wanted to</i>
<i>go down there with the crew,</i>

01:10:12.875 --> 01:10:15.502
<i>I suggested that</i>
<i>he call her first.</i>

01:10:15.586 --> 01:10:18.464
{\an1}- We could.
You have her number?

01:10:18.547 --> 01:10:21.175
-<i> So I moved our car</i>
<i>out of sight around the corner</i>

01:10:21.258 --> 01:10:23.260
<i>and dialed Frances' number</i>
<i>into Bill's phone</i>

01:10:23.344 --> 01:10:27.848
<i>so he could</i>
<i>make the call.</i>

01:10:27.932 --> 01:10:28.933
You ready?

01:10:29.016 --> 01:10:32.144
- Ready.

01:10:37.358 --> 01:10:40.277
<i>[line trilling]</i>

01:10:41.403 --> 01:10:42.738
-<i> Hello. Munroes.</i>

01:10:42.821 --> 01:10:45.407
- Hello, Frances?

01:10:45.491 --> 01:10:46.533
-<i> Yes.</i>

01:10:46.617 --> 01:10:47.660
- How are you?

01:10:47.743 --> 01:10:48.494
-<i> Fine.</i>
<i>Who's calling?</i>

01:10:48.577 --> 01:10:51.622
- Well, I want you
to guess.

01:10:51.705 --> 01:10:53.290
-<i> Oh, I can't.</i>
<i>[laughs]</i>

01:10:53.374 --> 01:10:54.959
<i>I don't know.</i>

01:10:55.042 --> 01:10:57.503
- Well, you think hard.

01:10:57.586 --> 01:11:00.589
Doesn't my voice
sound familiar to you?

01:11:02.466 --> 01:11:04.343
-<i> No.</i>

01:11:04.426 --> 01:11:05.719
- No?

01:11:05.803 --> 01:11:07.471
-<i> No.</i>

01:11:07.554 --> 01:11:10.391
- It's been a long time,
Frances.

01:11:12.977 --> 01:11:14.687
-<i> Yeah, you've got me</i>
<i>wondering now.</i>

01:11:14.770 --> 01:11:18.232
<i>Who is this?</i>

01:11:18.315 --> 01:11:18.816
<i>Hello?</i>

01:11:18.899 --> 01:11:20.859
- Yeah, I'm here.

01:11:20.943 --> 01:11:23.112
-<i> Okay.</i>

01:11:23.195 --> 01:11:24.071
{\an1}- Uh...

01:11:24.154 --> 01:11:25.197
- Tell her.

01:11:25.280 --> 01:11:27.241
- You don't know who I am?

01:11:27.324 --> 01:11:28.200
Think hard.

01:11:28.283 --> 01:11:32.538
I don't sound familiar
to you?

01:11:32.621 --> 01:11:33.831
-<i> No.</i>

01:11:33.914 --> 01:11:36.792
<i>Oh, wait a minute.</i>

01:11:36.875 --> 01:11:37.710
<i>Is this Jim Beckley?</i>

01:11:37.793 --> 01:11:40.045
- Who?

01:11:40.129 --> 01:11:41.463
-<i> Beckley?</i>

01:11:41.547 --> 01:11:42.589
- No.

01:11:42.673 --> 01:11:43.716
-<i> No?</i>

01:11:43.799 --> 01:11:47.219
<i>Oh.</i>

01:11:47.302 --> 01:11:48.470
- Tell her
who you are.

01:11:48.554 --> 01:11:49.888
{\an1}- Yeah.

01:11:49.972 --> 01:11:53.475
All right, I'm gonna
tell you who I am.

01:11:53.559 --> 01:11:54.601
-<i> Okay.</i>

01:11:54.685 --> 01:11:57.604
- Bill Heath.

01:11:59.565 --> 01:12:01.066
Hello?

01:12:01.150 --> 01:12:02.443
-<i> Hello.</i>

01:12:02.526 --> 01:12:04.445
- Bill Heath.

01:12:04.528 --> 01:12:06.280
-<i> Bill Heath?</i>

01:12:06.363 --> 01:12:09.742
- H-E-A-T-H.

01:12:09.825 --> 01:12:11.785
-<i> Okay.</i>
<i>Hi, Bill, how are you?</i>

01:12:11.869 --> 01:12:14.121
- You remember me now,
don't you?

01:12:14.204 --> 01:12:16.165
-<i> Yes, I do.</i>
<i>Of course I do.</i>

01:12:16.248 --> 01:12:18.625
<i>Well, what are you</i>
<i>up to?</i>

01:12:18.709 --> 01:12:19.960
- Oh, trying to do right.

01:12:20.044 --> 01:12:22.629
-<i> [laughs]</i>

01:12:22.713 --> 01:12:24.757
<i>Okay, is that hard?</i>

01:12:24.840 --> 01:12:28.135
- So--but I, you know,
I've been thinking about you

01:12:28.218 --> 01:12:31.847
a lot of the times,
and I said finally,

01:12:31.930 --> 01:12:34.391
you know, I'm just
gonna call you

01:12:34.475 --> 01:12:36.477
and--
-<i> Okay.</i>

01:12:36.560 --> 01:12:38.103
- So--

01:12:38.187 --> 01:12:39.938
-<i> So what's going on</i>
<i>in your life?</i>

01:12:40.022 --> 01:12:41.648
- I'm out in LA now,

01:12:41.732 --> 01:12:44.443
still working as
an actor out there.

01:12:44.526 --> 01:12:47.071
-<i> Well, good for you.</i>

01:12:47.154 --> 01:12:49.156
<i>Good for you.</i>
- So--

01:12:49.239 --> 01:12:51.325
-<i> That's what you</i>
<i>always wanted to do.</i>

01:12:51.408 --> 01:12:52.826
- Right.

01:12:52.910 --> 01:12:53.786
-<i> Do you have</i>
<i>any children?</i>

01:12:53.869 --> 01:12:56.455
- No, I--

01:12:56.538 --> 01:12:59.625
I should have
married you maybe.

01:12:59.708 --> 01:13:01.752
You know--
you know how it is.

01:13:01.835 --> 01:13:03.587
-<i> [laughs]</i>

01:13:03.670 --> 01:13:05.839
<i>Well, I have</i>
<i>nine grandchildren.</i>

01:13:05.923 --> 01:13:08.050
{\an1}- Really?

01:13:08.133 --> 01:13:10.385
-<i> Yes.</i>
- So--

01:13:10.469 --> 01:13:14.598
-<i> No, I'm a--I'm a grandmother</i>
<i>with nine grandchildren,</i>

01:13:14.681 --> 01:13:18.435
<i>and we have</i>
<i>twin granddaughters</i>

01:13:18.519 --> 01:13:22.147
<i>that are almost</i>
<i>three years old.</i>

01:13:22.231 --> 01:13:24.608
-<i> As the call went on,</i>
<i>15 minutes in,</i>

01:13:24.691 --> 01:13:26.568
<i>Bill still hadn't mentioned</i>
<i>to Frances</i>

01:13:26.652 --> 01:13:29.196
<i>that he was</i>
<i>right outside of her house.</i>

01:13:29.279 --> 01:13:31.657
- What do you remember most
about my mother?

01:13:31.740 --> 01:13:34.243
-<i> What do I remember most</i>
<i>about your mother?</i>

01:13:34.326 --> 01:13:35.744
<i>She didn't like me.</i>

01:13:35.828 --> 01:13:37.871
- Oh! What?

01:13:37.955 --> 01:13:39.039
-<i> She didn't.</i>

01:13:39.123 --> 01:13:41.125
- Why do you say that?

01:13:41.208 --> 01:13:43.043
-<i> Well, it's true.</i>

01:13:43.127 --> 01:13:44.503
- What makes you
say that?

01:13:44.586 --> 01:13:46.255
-<i> Why would she say it?</i>

01:13:46.338 --> 01:13:48.423
<i>I don't know,</i>
<i>but she--she didn't.</i>

01:13:50.134 --> 01:13:54.096
- Well, are you happy?

01:13:54.179 --> 01:13:57.349
-<i> Am I happy?</i>
<i>Yes, I'm happy.</i>

01:13:57.432 --> 01:13:58.433
<i>Why?</i>

01:13:58.517 --> 01:14:00.853
- You're on your second
marriage, right?

01:14:00.936 --> 01:14:04.982
-<i> Mm-hmm.</i>

01:14:05.065 --> 01:14:07.818
- Good grief.
Doesn't seem possible.

01:14:07.901 --> 01:14:09.069
How many years has it been?

01:14:09.153 --> 01:14:10.654
-<i> Well, let's see.</i>

01:14:10.737 --> 01:14:13.991
<i>Dave and I have been married</i>
<i>for almost 47--</i>

01:14:14.074 --> 01:14:17.369
<i>oh, we have been married</i>
<i>47 years.</i>

01:14:17.452 --> 01:14:21.081
- Mm.

01:14:21.165 --> 01:14:23.208
Well, the years go by.

01:14:23.292 --> 01:14:24.460
<i>- They do go by.</i>

01:14:24.543 --> 01:14:27.754
- The snap of a finger,
they go by.

01:14:27.838 --> 01:14:29.006
-<i> [laughs]</i>

01:14:29.089 --> 01:14:31.925
- Have you thought about me much
through the years?

01:14:32.009 --> 01:14:35.304
-<i> Of course.</i>

01:14:35.387 --> 01:14:38.891
- Do you ever want to pick up
the phone and call me?

01:14:38.974 --> 01:14:41.560
-<i> Of course.</i>

01:14:41.643 --> 01:14:44.563
- But you never did.

01:14:46.356 --> 01:14:49.735
Was it hard?

01:14:49.818 --> 01:14:51.403
Hello?

01:14:51.487 --> 01:14:52.946
-<i> Hello.</i>

01:14:53.030 --> 01:14:56.033
- Was it hard
to do that?

01:14:59.870 --> 01:15:01.246
Can you hear me,
Frances?

01:15:01.330 --> 01:15:04.416
-<i> Yes, I can--</i>
<i>Yes, I can hear you.</i>

01:15:04.917 --> 01:15:08.587
- Well--

01:15:08.670 --> 01:15:10.505
well, I just--

01:15:10.589 --> 01:15:12.299
you've been on my mind
so much,

01:15:12.382 --> 01:15:14.760
and I just had to
call you...

01:15:14.843 --> 01:15:15.761
-<i> Well, thank you.</i>

01:15:15.844 --> 01:15:18.597
- You know, just to hear
your voice.

01:15:18.680 --> 01:15:22.017
My life is--

01:15:22.100 --> 01:15:25.771
it's cheered me up, so...

01:15:25.854 --> 01:15:28.023
-<i> Well, good for you.</i>
<i>Are you all right?</i>

01:15:28.106 --> 01:15:30.108
- Am I all right?

01:15:30.192 --> 01:15:32.027
-<i> Mm-hmm.</i>
<i>Your health-wise?</i>

01:15:32.110 --> 01:15:32.986
- Yes.

01:15:33.070 --> 01:15:35.989
Knock on the wood.

01:15:36.073 --> 01:15:37.741
-<i> [laughs]</i>

01:15:37.824 --> 01:15:40.702
<i>Well, listen,</i>
<i>you take care of yourself.</i>

01:15:40.786 --> 01:15:42.496
<i>It's nice</i>
<i>to hear from you,</i>

01:15:42.579 --> 01:15:44.665
<i>and...</i>

01:15:44.748 --> 01:15:46.792
<i>may God bless you.</i>

01:15:46.875 --> 01:15:49.086
- And what was that again?

01:15:49.169 --> 01:15:51.129
-<i> I said,</i>
<i>and may God bless you.</i>

01:15:51.213 --> 01:15:52.923
- Oh, thank you.
The same to you.

01:15:53.006 --> 01:15:54.466
-<i> Thank you, Bill.</i>

01:15:54.549 --> 01:15:56.051
- Bye-bye. God bless.
<i>[line clicks]</i>

01:15:56.134 --> 01:15:59.680
[phone beeps]

01:15:59.763 --> 01:16:02.891
- All right.

01:16:02.975 --> 01:16:04.268
How do you feel?

01:16:04.351 --> 01:16:06.728
- How do I feel?

01:16:06.812 --> 01:16:08.814
{\an1}- [laughs] You know,
about the conversation.

01:16:08.897 --> 01:16:10.148
- How do you feel?

01:16:10.232 --> 01:16:11.650
- You seemed more
nervous than I--

01:16:11.733 --> 01:16:14.611
I wasn't nervous, was I?
I didn't seem nervous.

01:16:28.750 --> 01:16:30.669
- Do you still want to
go inside?

01:16:30.752 --> 01:16:31.503
- No, I don't think so.

01:16:31.586 --> 01:16:33.714
{\an1}I talked to her,
that's enough.

01:16:33.797 --> 01:16:38.176
I couldn't marry her.
It wouldn't work now.

01:16:41.138 --> 01:16:44.266
- Do you feel like
she's over you?

01:16:45.225 --> 01:16:47.978
<i>[somber music]</i>

01:16:48.061 --> 01:16:50.981
- Well, she sounded like it,
like it was just memories or--

01:16:51.064 --> 01:16:52.816
♪ ♪

01:16:52.899 --> 01:16:55.027
She didn't even recognize
my voice.

01:16:55.110 --> 01:16:58.989
♪ ♪

01:16:59.072 --> 01:17:00.032
- You okay?

01:17:00.115 --> 01:17:02.326
- Yeah.

01:17:02.409 --> 01:17:05.704
- You want to
go home?

01:17:05.787 --> 01:17:06.204
- Yeah.

01:17:06.288 --> 01:17:14.171
♪ ♪

01:17:16.048 --> 01:17:18.258
-<i> When we got back to</i>
<i>the hotel that night,</i>

01:17:18.342 --> 01:17:20.927
<i>there was a bee</i>
<i>on the loose...</i>

01:17:21.011 --> 01:17:22.179
{\an1}- Oop!

01:17:22.262 --> 01:17:25.557
<i>- And Bill seemed determined</i>
<i>to get it.</i>

01:17:25.640 --> 01:17:31.772
♪ ♪

01:17:35.901 --> 01:17:37.569
{\an1}- [sighs]

01:17:37.652 --> 01:17:39.780
He won't give up.

01:17:39.863 --> 01:17:40.280
[bleep]!

01:17:40.364 --> 01:17:42.115
Excuse me.

01:17:42.199 --> 01:17:49.122
♪ ♪

01:17:49.206 --> 01:17:51.249
[toilet flushes]

01:17:51.333 --> 01:17:55.128
All right,
down the toilet.

01:17:55.212 --> 01:17:57.381
- Good work.

01:17:59.299 --> 01:18:02.302
-<i> After spending so much time</i>
<i>in Arkansas,</i>

01:18:02.386 --> 01:18:03.762
<i>I found myself digging my way</i>
<i>out of all the other work</i>

01:18:03.845 --> 01:18:06.348
<i>that had piled up</i>
<i>in Los Angeles.</i>

01:18:06.431 --> 01:18:08.266
<i>I was working late hours</i>

01:18:08.350 --> 01:18:11.436
<i>and finding it hard to</i>
<i>adjust back to my routine.</i>

01:18:11.520 --> 01:18:13.939
<i>Bill wasn't really</i>
<i>on my mind much anymore.</i>

01:18:14.022 --> 01:18:16.191
<i>I think a part of me</i>
<i>wanted to believe</i>

01:18:16.274 --> 01:18:17.984
<i>that he would find</i>
<i>a happy ending,</i>

01:18:18.068 --> 01:18:19.986
<i>and when that</i>
<i>didn't happen,</i>

01:18:20.070 --> 01:18:21.738
<i>it was</i>
<i>a bit of a bummer.</i>

01:18:21.822 --> 01:18:23.824
<i>Then one day,</i>
<i>out of the blue,</i>

01:18:23.907 --> 01:18:26.493
<i>Bill asked to come by the</i>
<i>office to give me something.</i>

01:18:26.576 --> 01:18:28.036
{\an3}- I got something
for you.

01:18:28.120 --> 01:18:29.204
{\an1}- Really?

01:18:29.287 --> 01:18:30.580
This is for me?

01:18:30.664 --> 01:18:31.123
{\an3}- Yes.

01:18:31.206 --> 01:18:34.209
- What is it?

01:18:34.292 --> 01:18:37.212
Wow.
Thank you, Bill.

01:18:37.295 --> 01:18:40.006
Is this
a serving tray?

01:18:40.090 --> 01:18:41.216
- Yeah, you can put
pasta on there,

01:18:41.299 --> 01:18:45.470
salads, anything.

01:18:45.554 --> 01:18:47.305
- Wow.

01:18:47.389 --> 01:18:49.975
- I know the salesman,
and we picked it out.

01:18:50.058 --> 01:18:53.645
We thought that
that would be

01:18:53.728 --> 01:18:55.313
appropriate for you.

01:18:55.397 --> 01:18:57.190
- This is really sweet of you
to give this to me.

01:18:57.274 --> 01:18:59.067
- Of course.

01:18:59.151 --> 01:19:02.320
That's a small token for what--
what you've done.

01:19:02.404 --> 01:19:05.157
I appreciate everything.

01:19:05.240 --> 01:19:07.159
-<i> The tray was really nice,</i>
<i>but I discovered</i>

01:19:07.242 --> 01:19:09.161
<i>that Bill wasn't just here</i>
<i>to say thanks.</i>

01:19:09.244 --> 01:19:12.289
- What are your thoughts on that
actress that came from LA

01:19:12.372 --> 01:19:15.250
to Arkansas?

01:19:15.333 --> 01:19:16.334
- June?

01:19:16.418 --> 01:19:19.337
I thought she was good.

01:19:19.421 --> 01:19:20.547
- Well, just--
[laughs]

01:19:20.630 --> 01:19:22.048
- What do you mean?
What did you think of her?

01:19:22.132 --> 01:19:24.009
- Well, you know...

01:19:24.092 --> 01:19:26.845
she'd be a good contact
for me.

01:19:26.928 --> 01:19:28.346
- Why are you smiling, Bill?

01:19:28.430 --> 01:19:30.265
- [laughs]
I don't--

01:19:30.348 --> 01:19:32.058
- Do you have a crush
on her, Bill?

01:19:32.142 --> 01:19:34.060
- I didn't say
a crush on--

01:19:34.144 --> 01:19:35.103
- Do you have a crush
on June?

01:19:35.187 --> 01:19:37.564
- I worked with her one time.
[laughs]

01:19:37.647 --> 01:19:39.649
- Why are you laughing?
Look at you, Bill.

01:19:39.733 --> 01:19:40.692
You're blushing.

01:19:40.775 --> 01:19:42.194
Oh, my God.

01:19:42.277 --> 01:19:44.863
- I don't know what
her phone number is, so...

01:19:44.946 --> 01:19:46.823
- You want to call her
right now?

01:19:46.907 --> 01:19:48.617
- Yeah.

01:19:48.700 --> 01:19:50.869
<i>[line trilling]</i>

01:19:54.789 --> 01:19:56.541
-<i> Hello.</i>

01:19:56.625 --> 01:19:58.043
- June?

01:19:58.126 --> 01:19:59.127
-<i> Yes.</i>

01:19:59.211 --> 01:20:00.128
